sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as User
participant Client as WebClient
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant AuthSvc as AuthService
participant UserAuthDb as MongoUserAuth

Note over User,UserAuthDb: Luong 1 - Dang ky tai khoan
User->>Client: Nhap email, mat khau, ho ten, ngay sinh
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/auth/register
Gateway->>AuthSvc: Forward payload
AuthSvc->>UserAuthDb: Validate + tao UserAuth (inactive, unverified)
alt Hop le
  AuthSvc-->>Gateway: 201 + huong dan verify email
  Gateway-->>Client: Dang ky thanh cong
else Email trung / mat khau yeu / DOB sai
  AuthSvc-->>Gateway: 400/409
  Gateway-->>Client: Thong bao loi nghiep vu
end
